---

<Layout title="Feng Shui Products - SERENA">
  <section id="products-page" class="min-h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-slate-900 to-black relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- 背景装饰 -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-8 py-20">
      <!-- 顶部文字区域 -->
      <div class="mb-20 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-light text-white mb-6 tracking-wide">
          FENG SHUI <span class="font-semibold">PRODUCTS</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          从基础学习到深度体验，选择最适合你的风水服务方案。悬停卡片可查看详细信息。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 产品卡片网格 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
        {products.map((product) => (
          <ProductCard product={product} />
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- 底部说明 -->
      <div class="mt-20 text-center">
        <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-4">
          所有课程均由专业师资团队精心设计。支持一对一定制服务。
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/30 text-xs">
          点击卡片背面的"立即支付"按钮进行报名和支付。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  #products-page {
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 50px 50px;
  }
</style>
